{"type": "article", "id": 27228, "title": "极简木质家具", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-24T06:49:03Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702134125yL3S94YmIMhrGtWd.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>在家里放上巨石会是怎样一种景象？在设计师 Anna Bera 的构想中，它们不仅没有那么冷冰冰，反而营造出了极简的美感。最近她所创立的工作室 <a href=\"http://www.thewholeelements.com/\">The Whole Elements</a> 就推出了能够以假乱真的模块型木质家具 <a href=\"http://www.thewholeelements.com/#!esw/h0b8m\">Earth Stone Wood</a>，这些不规则的家具可以独立当作桌椅使用，也可以经过组合变成一个橱柜。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021341232xgNFC5oyl6MqsXv.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134123Y9CAkQnJfbRVTU8r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134124t1Gfzl3dILKScD8F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134125bmP94AdiLwanh2VB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}